<section sectnbr = "7B">
<servcat sctnbr = "07" scnbr = "02">
<configtype typenbr = "3">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "ASPAP70B7236024" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Inspección del actuador de regulación de temperatura 
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "ASPAP70B7236023">Extracción e instalación del actuador de regulación de temperatura:Tipo automático</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Fije el brazo al actuador y compruebe si el brazo funciona suavemente cuando la tensión de la batería se dirige a los terminales del conector del actuador (1). 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<title>
Funcionamiento del actuador de control de temperatura 
</title>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A722009S.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.766mm" ver = "01" gw = "203" gh = "119"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Con un ohmímetro, mida la resistencia entre el terminal &#34;3&#34; y el terminal &#34;5&#34; del conector del actuador (1) en cada posición del brazo. 
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Resistencia del actuador de control de temperatura 
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "1.312in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.147in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Posición del brazo 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Resistencia (25 &#176;C (77 &#176;F)) 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
MAX COOL [a] 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Aproximadamente 2,4 k&#937;
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
MAX HOT [b] 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Aproximadamente 4,8 k&#937;
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Utilice un ohmímetro para medir la resistencia entre el terminal &#34;1&#34; y el terminal &#34;3&#34;. 
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Si el resultado de la inspección no es el especificado, sustituya el actuador de control de temperatura. 
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Resistencia del actuador de control de temperatura (resistencia total) 
</title>
<ptxt>
6 k&#937;
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A722010.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "74.781mm" ver = "01" gw = "148" gh = "195"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.830in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.805in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
&#34;a&#34;: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
60&#176;
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Brazo 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Actuador de control de temperatura 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
</entry>
